channel.title: Jamie Johnson
channel.desc: It's Sports Personality of the Year time at Kingsmount Academy, and school captain Dillon is confident of winning. Boggy finally has a date with online buddy Nancy and enlists Indira's help to prepare. The date doesn't go as planned and Boggy feels humiliated, so his friends decide to step up. The Kingsmount SPOTY trophy is in their sights but who will eventually triumph.
